Package risingWaters

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Driver
    Runs the game
    HighScores
    Displays the top 10 high scores.
    Instructions
    Displays the instructions for this game
    Introduction
    Displays the intro for this game.
    Level1
    Displays room 1 of the game where the user learns how to prepare for a flood.
    Level2
    This class represents the second level.
    Level3
    Displays room 3 of the game where the user must escape the flood area to safety.
    LoadingScreen
    Creates a loading image and animation
    MainMenu
    This class represents the home screen which will redirect to all the other screens.
    Player
    This program represents a player of the game
    ProcessEnding
    After the user has completed the game, this program processes their performance and displays the appropriate ending.
    Quit
    Displays the quit screen and closes the program.
    ResourceLoader
    Loads resources from files.
